channel.title: Port already in use?
channel.description:
Okay, i have fr33sc4p3 pkz downloaded.. i have nothing else running, then i click on runserver and get this?:
Error: Unable to startup listener on 43594 - port already in use?
but i dont have any ports open besides the runserver?

item.title: Port already in use?
item.dc:creator: @Vince2 Vince,
item.description:
@Vince2 wrote:

Do you have a MoparScape client open? & CTRL + Alt + Del, (or right click > Task Manager), and look for all the “java.exe” processes (processes tab), and “End Process”, then try again.
